<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/bootstrap.min.css" />
    <title>Articles</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h2 style="text-align: center">Welcome to blog club</h2>

   <div>
    <center>
        <a href="/signup"><button style="padding:10px">Signup</button></a>
        <a href="/login"><button style="padding:10px">Login</button></a>
    </center>
   </div>

    <p style="margin-top:30px; text-align:justify; padding:30px;">
      Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry.
